WorkItem.Description: I have all filters enabled except Options, I-Filter and All, yet I cannot get Darkmoon Cards to show up under trinkets unless they are already equipped from a downloaded or saved profile.
WorkItem.Summary: [ItemFilters] Darkmoon Cards Not Showing Under Trinkets

Comments.Message: Interesting, running "Tools>Update Item Cache from the Armory" did not fix the issue, but running "Tools>Update Item Cache from Wowhead" appears to have fixed the issue.  Is this working as intended?

Yeah this was due to NULL item information being filtered into the "ALL" tab. The "ALL" tab has been temporarily removed as a fix in 2.2.21.

As it is now, all NULL items will default to the "Other" tab, so be sure to check items in the "Other" tab to see if the information can be refreshed from the other source (Wowhead/Armory).
